commit_message: data commit to share with Cliff
Bulk commit to sync with mac
changed the mismatch threshold to 15 from 10
Added a module for trimming high missmatch edges of reads before assembly.
a bulk push plots in the paper.
added a working version of SimilarityPlotter.
keep the summary files for reference comparison
Fixed a bug which causes a shift in amino acid sequences.
changed the script to properly orient the alignments based on transcript strand.
added a filtration step to the script for samples that are not covered more than %50 of the Ref gene.
changed the output file name variable
added dNdS calculation module and resources.
presented the PerlLibs to perl scripts.
Added some useful perl scripts and changed the chmod +x.
added two previous versions of jbamtools
added some functions to msa file analysis scripts.
changed the clustal output of mafft
replaced msa from clustal to mafft vfat annotate.pl.
added more function in stats scripts.
Fixed a bug in python code for removing low coverage edges of contigs.
added a test script to assess EBV typing sensitivity
added isoform to gene tables for EBV transcripts.
modified qualify checker and fixer for genome scaffolds.
Simlified some of the functions, such as flexbed.
Added lower and ceiling coverage threshold for concensus base call.
fixed unsorted bam file for picards
modified the assembly quality checking scripts.
